msgctxt "sn45.42-47:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:0.2"
msgid "5. Aññatitthiyapeyyālavagga "
msgstr "5. Abbreviated Texts on Followers of Other Paths "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 42–47. Saṃyojanappahānādisuttachakka → ñāṇadassanasuttaṃ (bj) | ñāṇaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:0.3"
msgid "42–47. Saṃyojanappahānādisuttachakka "
msgstr "42–47. Six Discourses on Giving Up Fetters, Etc. "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:1.1"
msgid "“Sace vo, bhikkhave, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, if wanderers who follow another path were to ask you: "

msgctxt "sn45.42-47:1.2"
msgid "‘kimatthiyaṃ, āvuso, samaṇe gotame brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti, evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, bhikkhave, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyātha: "
msgstr "‘Reverends, what’s the purpose of living the spiritual life with the ascetic Gotama?’ You should answer them like this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:1.3"
msgid "‘saṃyojanappahānatthaṃ kho, āvuso, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti … pe … "
msgstr "‘The purpose of living the spiritual life under the Buddha is to give up the fetters.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:1.4"
msgid "‘anusayasamugghātanatthaṃ kho, āvuso, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti … pe … "
msgstr "‘… to uproot the underlying tendencies.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:1.5"
msgid "‘addhānapariññatthaṃ kho, āvuso, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti … pe … "
msgstr "‘… to completely understand the course of time.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:1.6"
msgid "‘āsavānaṃ khayatthaṃ kho, āvuso, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti … pe … "
msgstr "‘… to end the defilements.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:1.7"
msgid "‘vijjāvimuttiphalasacchikiriyatthaṃ kho, āvuso, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti … pe … "
msgstr "‘… to realize the fruit of knowledge and freedom.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:1.8"
msgid "‘ñāṇadassanatthaṃ kho, āvuso, bhagavati brahmacariyaṃ vussatī’ti … pe …. "
msgstr "‘… for knowledge and vision.’ …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.42-47:1.9"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

